# 处理时间格式
for item in item_info.find({},{'pub_time':1,'_id':1}):
    print(item)
    pub_date_str = item['pub_time'].split(' ') [0].split('-')
    length = len(pub_date_str)
    print(item)
    print(pub_date_str)
    print(length)
    if length >1:
        
        month = int(pub_date_str[0])
        day = int(pub_date_str[1])
        if month >1:
            year = 2015
        else:
            year = 2016
        dates = '{}.{}.{}'.format(year,month,day)
        print(date)
        item_info.update_one({'_id':item['_id']},{'$set':{'pub_time':dates}})
    else :
        item_info.update_one({'_id':item['_id']},{'$set':{'pub_time':None}})

In [112]:
# 日期的月和日如果为个位数则前面补零
for item in item_info.find():
    if item['pub_time'] is not None:
        month = item['pub_time'].split('.')[1]
        day = item['pub_time'].split('.')[2]
        print(month)
        year =  item['pub_time'].split('.')[0]
        if len(month)==1:
            month = '0'+month
        if(len(day)==1):
            day = '0'+day
        date_str = '{}.{}.{}'.format(year, month, day) 
        print(date_str)
        item_info.update_one({'_id':item['_id']},{'$set':{'pub_time':date_str}})
        
    else:
        print(item['pub_time'])

# 获取两个时间段内的所有日期
def get_all_dates(date1,date2):
    start_date = date(int(date1.split('.')[0]),int(date1.split('.')[1]),int(date1.split('.')[2]))
    end_date = date(int(date2.split('.')[0]),int(date2.split('.')[1]),int(date2.split('.')[2]))
    days = timedelta(days=1)
    while start_date<=end_date:
        dates = start_date.strftime('%Y.%m.%d')
        yield dates
        start_date+=days

# 封装
def get_series(date1,date2,area):

        date_list = [date_str for date_str in get_all_dates(date1,date2)]
        pipline = [

            { '$match':{'pub_time':{'$in':date_list},'area':area}},
            {'$group':{

                      '_id':{'cate':'$cate'},
                    'count':{'$sum':1}
                }},
            {'$sort':{'count':-1}},
            {'$limit':3}
        ]

        for item in item_info.aggregate(pipline):
            data = {
                'name':item['_id']['cate'],
                'data':[item['count']],
                'type':'column'
            }
            yield data

# 获得所有的地区
def get_all_area(date1,date2):
    date_list = [date_str for date_str in get_all_dates(date1,date2)]
    pipline = [

        { '$match':{'pub_time':{'$in':date_list}},},
        {'$group':{

                  '_id':{'area':'$area'},
               
            }},
    
    ]
    area_list = []
    for i in item_info.aggregate(pipline):
        area_list.append(i['_id']['area'])
    
    return area_list
